      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "For sale is a well-maintained vehicle in good condition. This car has been reliably serviced and remains mechanically sound, offering a comfortable and confident driving experience. The exterior is in great shape with only minor surface scratches typical of careful use, and the interior has been kept clean and smoke-free. It is a dependable option for anyone seeking a quality pre-owned vehicle that has many miles left to give.",
