    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily commutes and weekend trips. It\u2019s got that 'just right' feel\u2014well-loved, runs like a dream, and still looks sharp on the road! If you're looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready for many more miles of adventures, you\u2019ve found it. Drop me a message if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
