      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of pride in ownership, offering a harmonious blend of performance and comfort. The exterior features a deep, lustrous finish that shines brilliantly in the sun, with only minor stone chips on the front fascia that attest to its time on the open road. The alloy wheels are clean and free of significant curbing, framing tires with ample tread remaining. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the leather upholstery is supple and free of tears, showing only light natural graining on the driver\u2019s bolster. All onboard electronics, from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control, operate flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, characterized by a smooth idle, responsive acceleration, and a transmission that shifts with precision. Having been serviced at regular intervals, this car is mechanically sound and aesthetically pleasing, ready to provide its next owner with a premium driving experience without the premium price tag.",
      "price": 34500.0,
